xt-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">IARC（国际癌症研究机构）：只负责贴标签（有没有可能致癌），不负责谈剂量。它列为 2B 类只代表“证据有限”，连泡菜和手机辐射都在这个类别里</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">JECFA（食品添加剂专家委员会）：才是负责定“安全标准”的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一步“定义校准”，直接把 90% 的无效焦虑过滤掉了</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二步：数据计算——拒绝模糊建议，直接上算术题</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100027999\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=335bcc53&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0X9RU0GzzcaYXGhwWkvyEYnR6gy8WYW0Hg62tDw3DMQicnxWIpicWgXno6zNpBdxxFPsHGhRZ57aSUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100028000\" data-ratio=\"0.3388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=386467d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0X9RU0GzzcaYXGhwWkvyEYnleQmFkpBJx5EBiccoicfWJ9yFDltCF1f8kz4N4KyEQL3Kcpyy6VwVKhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">普通的 AI 可能会说：“建议您适量饮用”。什么叫适量？MiroThinker 拒绝废话，直接运行python程序：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:1em;list-style:circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">• 设定你的体重</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;di